dc_description_s: This point data layer represents public land survey system corners (PLSS) for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Clark_PLSS_2018.gdb.[This dataset contains local PLSS locations and attributes collected by the county surveyor or another authorized entity using GPS and conventional surveying methodologies. These points are in The Clark County Coordinate System and have a county-wide extent. The County Surveyor serves as custodian for this data, and updates them as needed]
